{"title":"母亲","authors":["曼努艾尔·那瓦罗·鲁那"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":7,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔古巴〕曼努艾尔·那瓦罗·鲁那"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲跨入兵营，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿子已经服刑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是她那母亲的目光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却是骄傲没有悲伤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这些勇敢的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这些严肃的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着她，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感动得泪花满眶……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲平静地说道："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“他背叛了自己的祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪毙他，你们做得对呀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不过他的两个兄弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在跟我来到了兵营，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两个训练有素的兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将同你们一道去打击敌人。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我不想打听死鬼的情况，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我知道你们枪毙的是个叛徒；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是我要求你们向我保证："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一旦这两个小鬼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也背叛了祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们决不要饶恕他们。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她瞪着两个儿子的眼睛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对他们说道："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“去吧。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔吕翰译〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}